Light Sleeper;;1992;;R;;Crime,Drama;;6.9;;Paul Schrader;;Willem Dafoe,Susan Sarandon,Dana Delany,David Clennon,Mary Beth Hurt,Victor Garber,Jane Adams,Paul Jabara,Robert Cicchini,Sam Rockwell,Rene Rivera,David Spade,Steven Posen,Ken Ladd,Brian Judge,Vince Cupone,Chris Northup,Paul Stocker;;A drug dealer with upscale clientele is having moral problems going about his daily deliveries. A reformed addict, he has never gotten over the wife that left him, and the couple that use him for deliveries worry about his mental well-being and his effectiveness at his job. Meanwhile someone is killing women in apparently drug-related incidents.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0102307/